Add a group

sudo group add <group_name>


Add user in a particular group

sudo useradd -g <group_name> username


  <<======  
  sudo useradd -g gituser tester2
  sudo passwd tester2
  mkuserdir /home/tester2 tester2
  sudo mkuserdir /home/tester2 tester2
  sudo mkuserdir tester2 /home/tester2
  mkhomedir-helper tester2
  sudo mkhomedir-helper tester2
  sudo mkhomedir_helper tester2
  su - tester2
  sudo usermod -s /bin/bash tester2
  ========>>



